The above errata have been given, in order to free, as far as is now possible,
the Paper of 1787 from the errors indicated in the Note at the beginning of
Section VI. of the present Memoir. p. 201.; but that Paper cannot be rendered
so perfect as it ought to have been, unless some sheets of it are re-printed.
